## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of current data and the scope of the sources reviewed. Some articles may not provide comprehensive insights into all potential causes of domestic violence. Additionally, the complexity of individual cases means that not all factors can be generalized across all instances of domestic violence. Further research, including longitudinal studies and interviews with both victims and perpetrators, would provide a more nuanced understanding of this issue.

